{"sections":{"cover_rfCWrh":{"type":"cover","blocks":{"image_wTe7xN":{"type":"image","settings":{"desktop_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/61104HighRes.jpg","subtitle":"","title":"<p>Acerca de<br\/><strong>Schar<\/strong><\/p>","text_paragraph":"","button_label":"Conoce más de Schär","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["image_wTe7xN"],"name":"Portada Hero","settings":{"content_position":"bottom-center","text_alignment":"center","content_max_width":540,"section_height_desktop":70,"section_height_mobile":50,"section_max_height":800,"padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60,"overlay_color":"#2c1a0e","overlay_opacity":50,"heading_tag":"h2","title_size_desktop":72,"title_size_mobile":36,"title_line_height":105,"title_color":"#ffffff","title_margin_bottom":0,"subtitle_size_desktop":13,"subtitle_size_mobile":11,"subtitle_color":"#f5c842","subtitle_margin_bottom":12,"paragraph_size_desktop":18,"paragraph_size_mobile":14,"paragraph_color":"#ffffffe6","paragraph_margin_top":16,"button_bg_color":"#e8ddd0","button_text_color":"#2c1a0e","button_bg_hover":"#2c1a0e","button_text_hover":"#ffffff","button_border_radius":50,"button_height":48,"button_padding_x":32,"button_size_desktop":13,"button_size_mobile":12,"button_margin_top":32,"bottom_paragraph":""}},"text_image_icons_kKTJWg":{"type":"text-image-icons","name":"Texto + Imagen + Íconos","settings":{"image_position":"left","image_col_width":45,"title":"<p>Hecho con lo mejor<br\/>de nosotros<\/p>","text":"<p>En Schär, desde 1922 creemos que, por mucho que cambien las cosas, la comida siempre tendrá el poder de unirnos.<br\/><br\/>Y en los últimos tiempos, lo hemos podido comprobar. Por eso, estamos más convencidos que nunca de que cada persona tiene un lugar insustituible en la mesa.<br\/><br\/>La mejor manera de que todos se sientan como en casa es preparar una comida en la que todos participen. Por eso, en Schär, solo utilizamos los mejores cereales y granos para adaptarnos a los gustos y necesidades únicos de cada persona.<br\/><br\/>Porque para nosotros, lo más importante no es solo crear productos sin gluten, sino también elaborarlos con lo mejor de nosotros.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","button_label":"Conoce más aquí","button_link":"","text_alignment":"left","vertical_align":"center","content_gap":60,"text_max_width":600,"text_only_alignment":"center","text_only_max_width":700,"bg_color":"#e8ddd0","padding_top":80,"padding_bottom":80,"heading_tag":"h2","heading_size_desktop":56,"heading_size_mobile":32,"heading_line_height":110,"heading_color":"#2c1a0e","heading_margin_bottom":24,"text_size_desktop":20,"text_size_mobile":15,"text_color":"#2c1a0e","text_margin_top":20,"button_bg_color":"#2c1a0e","button_text_color":"#ffffff","button_bg_hover":"#c41e3a","button_text_hover":"#ffffff","button_border_radius":50,"button_height":48,"button_padding_x":32,"button_size_desktop":13,"button_size_mobile":12,"button_margin_top":32}},"image_with_texts_JNGKdg":{"type":"image-with-texts","custom_css":[],"name":"Imagen con textos","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/img-2.png","image_ratio":"square","image_custom_ratio":40,"image_position":"right","image_col_width":45,"heading":"<p><strong>Calidad<\/strong><\/p>","text_content":"<p>La calidad ha sido y siempre será el pilar de todo lo que hacemos. <\/p><p>Desde la selección de los mejores cereales sin gluten hasta el tiempo que dedicamos a nuestros clientes, la calidad se refleja en el esfuerzo invertido. <\/p><p>Esta variedad premium de ingredientes sin gluten llega a los platos de nuestros consumidores, a quienes invitamos a reunirse y disfrutar de momentos especiales alrededor de la mesa<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","vertical_align":"center","content_gap":20,"text_padding":20,"bg_color":"#e8ddd0","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60,"heading_tag":"h2","heading_size_desktop":72,"heading_size_mobile":32,"heading_line_height":110,"heading_color":"#c41e3a","text_size_desktop":18,"text_size_mobile":15,"text_color":"#2c1a0e","button_bg_color":"#2c1a0e","button_text_color":"#ffffff","button_bg_hover":"#c41e3a","button_text_hover":"#ffffff","button_border_radius":50,"button_size_desktop":14,"button_size_mobile":13,"button_margin_top":28}},"image_with_texts_TbR7Hq":{"type":"image-with-texts","custom_css":[],"name":"Imagen con textos","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/img-3.png","image_ratio":"square","image_custom_ratio":60,"image_position":"left","image_col_width":45,"heading":"<p><strong>Pasión<\/strong><\/p>","text_content":"<p>Desde nuestros agricultores comprometidos hasta nuestros panaderos artesanos, lo hacemos por amor al oficio. <\/p><p>Nos apasiona lo que hacemos; somos maestros, somos creadores, somos panaderos. <\/p><p>Creemos que la pasión prima sobre la perfección, siempre<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","vertical_align":"center","content_gap":20,"text_padding":20,"bg_color":"#F5F0EB","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60,"heading_tag":"h2","heading_size_desktop":72,"heading_size_mobile":32,"heading_line_height":110,"heading_color":"#6d6560","text_size_desktop":18,"text_size_mobile":15,"text_color":"#2c1a0e","button_bg_color":"#2c1a0e","button_text_color":"#ffffff","button_bg_hover":"#c41e3a","button_text_hover":"#ffffff","button_border_radius":50,"button_size_desktop":14,"button_size_mobile":13,"button_margin_top":28}},"image_with_texts_J8hVwj":{"type":"image-with-texts","custom_css":[],"name":"Imagen con textos","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/img-4.png","image_ratio":"square","image_custom_ratio":40,"image_position":"right","image_col_width":45,"heading":"<p><strong>Proximidad<\/strong><\/p>","text_content":"<p>Nos mantenemos cerca de nuestros consumidores porque sabemos que sus necesidades y gustos cambian constantemente y queremos cambiar con ellos. <\/p><p>La cercanía es la única manera de llegar lejos.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","vertical_align":"center","content_gap":20,"text_padding":20,"bg_color":"#e8ddd0","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60